                                         "text":  "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgPlanckCMB\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPlanckCMB', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figure 1</b>: Map of the cosmic microwave background (<htcite0>).</p>",
